        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <h3><a name="Summary"></a>Summary</h3>

<p>Research and implement application portability and simplified installation.</p>

<h3><a name="Context"></a>Context</h3>

<p>This issue focuses on enhancing the application by making it portable and simplifying the installation process.</p>

<h3><a name="Acceptancecriteria"></a>Acceptance criteria</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Application must be portable.</li>
	<li>Installation process should be simplified.</li>
</ul>

